some freelance stuff
next month.

06:01.667 --> 06:04.250
So you just stay
in touch, okay?

06:04.250 --> 06:05.458
Bye.
(MACHINE BEEPS)

06:05.458 --> 06:07.750
Mr. Rago, my name's Hakiem.

06:07.750 --> 06:12.417
