but Mom said she's broke
until next month.

06:23.875 --> 06:26.625
And that since you
just got that big new
Key Brands account,

06:26.625 --> 06:28.291
I had to ask you.

06:28.291 --> 06:29.792
So here it goes.

06:29.792 --> 06:32.667
There's an eclipse
coming up in Mexico,
and it's a really big deal.

06:32.667 --> 06:34.667
My whole astronomy
club is going.

06:34.667 --> 06:37.250
And if we get
the ticket early enough,
it'll be really cheap.

06:37.250 --> 06:41.333
And this is really
important to me.
I really, really want to go.

06:41.333 --> 06:42.959
