I could get unemployment
before I get social security?

08:28.875 --> 08:32.417
Have you previously
collected benefits?

08:32.417 --> 08:34.166
No. I've always had a job.

08:34.166 --> 08:38.291
Can you operate any
industrial machinery,
farm equipment?

08:39.958 --> 08:43.582
Yeah. That was a required
course in college.

08:43.582 --> 08:45.250
Theory of Plowing.

08:47.750 --> 08:50.000
I have all day, Bill.

08:50.000 --> 08:53.750
Now, why don't you
tell me what you'd
be willing to do?

08:53.750 --> 08:57.208
If you give me a check,
I'd be willing to cash it.

09:01.583 --> 09:03.417
Come here. Come here.

09:05.625 --> 09:07.417
Now, this is your first
time here, right?

09:08.792 --> 09:11.792
A man your age.
It can't be easy.

09:11.792 --> 09:14.125
You're humiliated.
You're frustrated.

09:14.125 --> 09:16.875
I see it on 100 people's
faces every day.

09:16.875 --> 09:18.792
And whether you
believe it or not,

09:18.792 --> 09:21.417
I feel for each
and every one of 'em.

09:22.917 --> 09:26.291
Now you can either
help me help you,

09:27.458 --> 09:28.417
or you can be an asshole.

09:29.625 --> 09:31.834
