and turn to dust.

09:38.333 --> 09:39.291
So...

09:39.625 --> 09:41.333
Let's begin again.

09:42.917 --> 09:46.291
Have you previously
collected benefits?

09:49.458 --> 09:50.917
No.

09:50.917 --> 09:53.333
What would you
be willing to do?

09:54.667 --> 09:56.333
Milk cows.

09:57.542 --> 09:59.375
Uh, shear sheep.

10:00.625 --> 10:03.041
Pluck chickens.
All right, Bill.

10:03.041 --> 10:06.333
