Jesus, when are you
gonna grow up?

10:42.625 --> 10:44.041
I am growin' up.

10:44.041 --> 10:46.041
You know it's what
I wanna do.

10:46.041 --> 10:48.208
Oh, there's the path
to big bucks.

10:48.208 --> 10:52.417
Starin' out into space.
Look! I discovered Venus.
Pay me.

10:53.875 --> 10:56.875
Astrology, maybe you could
make a few dollars,

10:56.875 --> 10:59.208
doin' people's horoscopes
or somethin'.

10:59.208 --> 11:02.750
