You want a frozen malt?
No.

11:06.583 --> 11:08.041
Gimme two.
Gimme two.

11:08.041 --> 11:11.083
Em. Wait a minute.
Em, come on.

11:11.083 --> 11:14.500
I'm sure you'll find
a very nice eclipse to
see around here someday.

11:14.500 --> 11:15.834
Yeah, in the year 2047!

11:15.834 --> 11:17.917
You want your pennant?

11:17.917 --> 11:20.542
EMILY: No, I just want you
to believe in me!

11:31.583 --> 11:34.250
