56:13.750 --> 56:15.417
Do I hear 'em
bangin' on the desk?

56:15.417 --> 56:19.333
No, this, fool!
(VOCALIZES)

56:19.333 --> 56:21.125
"This above..." Get up.

56:21.792 --> 56:24.583
"This above all,
to thine own self
be true." Say it.

56:24.583 --> 56:26.959
"This above all,
to thine own self be true."

56:26.959 --> 56:29.792
ALL: "This above all,
