Come on, Mel!

56:43.834 --> 56:46.041
"This above all,
to thine own self be true."
Go, Mel, go!

56:46.041 --> 56:49.625
"This above all,
to thine own self be true."
BILL: You got it!

56:49.625 --> 56:51.834
"This above all,
to thine own self be true."

56:51.834 --> 56:55.583
Way to go, Mel!
Give me five! Mel Melvin!

56:55.583 --> 56:57.583
(ALL CHEERING)
Yeehaw!

